      <title>Eclipse 使用月影面板将美国太阳能发电量削减 30 吉瓦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/eclipse-to-cut-us-solar-by-30-gigawatts-as-moon-shades-panels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周一的日全食期间，美国将损失超过 30 吉瓦的太阳能——大约相当于30个核反应堆的产量——因为在黄金发电时段阳光被阻挡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/eclipse-to-cut-us-solar-by-30-gigawatts-as-moon-shades-panels</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
